 <title>What&#039;s new</title>
 <link>http://www.watchmn.org/online-newsletters/autumn-2012/whats-new</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Board news&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; WATCH is pleased to welcome three new members to the board of directors.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Andrea Caro became interested in WATCH’s mission through the Management Assistance Project’s Best on Board program. Originally from Argentina, Andrea has more than 12 years of experience at Cummins, Inc., leading teams and developing, implementing, and evaluating business strategies across the U.S., Asia, Europe, and Latin America. She spearheads the Cummins United Way campaign and coordinates a sponsorship relationship between the company and a local nonprofit.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.watchmn.org/online-newsletters/autumn-2012/whats-new&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;read more&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
